title: Need a Jungler for a 2017 based ranked team,
body: Hi guys and gals, I already posted on the forums about making a ranked 5's team for 2017 and I am now only looking for a jungler. silver + is the requirement, must have a working headset and discord. We are in for the long haul so please only add me if you are willing to commit. Add me at your discretion :)
